///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Takes a user_id
Pulls all items from CartItems for that user
Validates that each copy is still AVAILABLE and has a price
Creates:
one row in Orders
one row per item in OrderItems
one simulated Payment
Marks the purchased Copies as SOLD
Clears the cart
Prints a clear summary

All in one transaction so it’s either all-or-nothing.